<aside class="success">
  Added in 4.5.0
</aside>

The _JSON Web Token (JWT) Profile for OAuth 2.0 Client Authentication and Authorization Grants_
allows to request an OAuth 2.0 access token with a JWT id_token bearer assertion. The flow is defined in
